snippet.title: Workin' Things Out
snippet.description:
Money, Career, Health, Family.  I'm just Workin' Things Out like everyone else.

For me it begins with my health.  I've started a diet and exercise VLOG to help keep myself motivated.

I would like to connect with others going through any of the same things I'm facing.  Please leave a Comment or Subscribe!
